00:06:39.260 --> 00:06:42.260
Tādēļ ir svarīgi atcerēties to, lai vai tas ir labs vai slikts --

00:06:42.260 --> 00:06:44.260
"This Too Shall Pass".

00:06:44.260 --> 00:06:46.260
Liels paldies!

00:06:46.260 --> 00:06:52.260
(Aplausi)

00:06:52.260 --> 00:06:54.260
